cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.DS, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and specifically super resolution of SEM images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of sparsity-based techniques also suggests a possible fit with cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
